From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 20:28:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: resolve 5 bugs across account, orders, admin, and cart
 pages

- AccountPage: fix profile fields empty on load (useEffect sync instead of stale useState init)
- AccountPage: use context signOut instead of bare lib/auth signOut (properly clears auth state)
- OrdersPage: fix infinite loading spinner when user is unauthenticated
- AdminProducts: replace broken edge function calls with direct Supabase (create, update, archive)
- AdminInventory: replace fragile edge function + fallback with direct Supabase upsert
- CartPage: add comment clarifying free delivery threshold logic
